<div id="review_2200191595" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2200191595" />
    <a title="Noor Jaber" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/18907811-noor-jaber"><img alt="Noor Jaber" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1364682443p2/18907811.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2200191595?book_show_action=true">Nov 30, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Noor Jaber" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Noor Jaber" href="/user/show/18907811-noor-jaber">Noor Jaber</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
                  <em>
                    This review has been hidden because it contains spoilers. To view it,
                    <a href="#" onclick="Effect.toggle(&#39;reviewTextContainer2200191595&#39;); return false;">click here.</a>
                  </em>
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2200191595" class="readable"
                    style="display:none"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9368355736374294026">A play that centers around reasoning and lies. It’s gloomy as the play consists of only three characters. The play deals with the struggles of torture and sexual assaults that one of the characters has experienced in the past. One of the overarching themes of this play is justice and reconciliation. The play is an amazing read, short, and quick to the point. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


