<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer4831573144711804574">Vladimiro Ariel Dorfman is an Argentine-Chilean novelist, playwright, essayist, academic, and human rights activist. A citizen of the United States since 2004, he has been a professor of literature and Latin American Studies at Duke University, in Durham, North Carolina since 1985.<br/><br/></span>

